Typical spark-submit command:
        $ spark-submit --class spark.sql.DriverJDBC --master local[*] SparkCourse.jar

Spark-submit including external libraries:
        $ spark-submit --class spark.sql.DriverJDBC --master local[*] --jars Downloads/postgresql-42.2.5.jar --driver-class-path Downloads/postgresql-42.2.5.jar SparkCourse.jar

Start Postgres SQL server:
		$ service postgresql-11 start

Stop Postgres SQL server:
		$ service postgresql-11 stop

Start thrift server watcher:         
        $ start-thriftserver.sh --hiveconf hive.server2.thrift.port=12000 --hiveconf hive.server2.thrift.bind.host=0.0.0.0 --master local[*]

Stop thrift server:
		$ stop-thriftserver.sh

